188
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:18,900
Saya boleh menghidupkan awak kembali.

189
00:11:22,110 --> 00:11:24,210
Sangat perkasa awak.

190
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:28,420
By the way, bos,

191
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:30,280
