222
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,610
Perlawanan hari ini akan bermula.

223
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:54,416
Murid-murid Lapan Istana yang paling dihargai

224
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,800
