225
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:58,330
Guru Sekte Shi dan lapan ketua istana

226
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,090
mungkin akan berada di sana juga.

227
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:02,630
Guru Besar,

228
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,900
